description:
Danny welcomes the amazing/hilarious Lauren Ash (NBC's Superstore) to recap the season premiere of TLC's 90 Day Fiance, and also talks to stars from the franchise-- Darcey (Before the 90 Days), Paul (Before the 90 Days), and Danielle/Ashley/Jay/Jonathan/Fernanda (90 Day). Danny also recaps his run-in with Queen Reba McEntire. Everything Iconic with be back to Housewives next Thursday!
